---
title: Za'atar Lamb Bowls with Hummus and Spiced Rice
description: Shawarma-spiced rice is jeweled with roasted peppers and onions, then topped with fragrant za'atar-spiced lamb, hummus and fresh tomato. Grab a fork and dig in
